nodes.text: The Imperial Most Wanted List existed around 3 ABY and contained the names and bounties of thousands of creatures wanted by the Imperial Navy and Imperial Army.

Rebel Alliance members Luke Skywalker and Lando Calrissian were high on the Empire's list of most-wanted outlaws. Celia Durasha earned a spot on the list after her actions trying to help the Alliance agent Detien Kaileel aboard the Kuari Princess.
